---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  titulo="David Varea | Marketing centrado en rentabilidad"
  canonical="/"
  ogTitle="🤝 David Varea"
  ogDescription="El director de marketing en las sombras"
  ogUrl="https://davidvarea.com"
>
  <main class="stage">
    <section class="hero-card">
      <div class="hero-photo-wrap">
        <img
          class="hero-photo"
          src="/imgs/profile-pic.webp"
          alt="David Varea"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero-headline">
        Mis clientes han facturado
        <span class="hl-squiggle">
          <span class="squiggle-text">2.4 millones</span>
          <svg
            class="squiggle-svg"
            viewBox="0 0 140 10"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M2 5 Q 35 1 70 5 T 138 5"
              stroke-width="2.4"
              fill="none"
              stroke-linecap="round"
            />
          </svg>
        </span>
        de € con mi ayuda
      </h1>

      <div class="postit-wrap">
        <div class="postit">
          <span class="tape" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Este título es para mí mismo, para
          <span class="bold">fascinar al David Varea de hace 3 años.</span>
          No sabía ni qué significaba funnel y quiso ser autodidacta..
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-heading">
      <span class="caret">▾</span>
      Qué te trae por aquí
    </div>

    <nav class="blocks" aria-label="Secciones">
      <svg
        class="arrow-doodle"
        viewBox="0 0 100 100"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <path
          d="M 92 6 Q 28 48 35 92"
          stroke-width="2.8"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
        />
        <path
          d="M 35 92 L 23 80"
          stroke-width="2.8"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
        />
        <path
          d="M 35 92 L 49 82"
          stroke-width="2.8"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
        />
      </svg>

      <a
        class="block block--primary"
        href="/director"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        draggable="false"
      >
        <span class="handle" aria-hidden="true">⋮⋮</span>
        <img class="icon" src="/imgs/svg/handshake.svg" alt="🤝" />
        <span class="body">
          <span class="title">Mis servicios B2B</span>
          <span class="subtitle-hand">CMO en las sombras + Copywriter</span>
        </span>
        <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>

      <a
        class="block block--secondary"
        href="mapa"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        draggable="false"
      >
        <span class="handle" aria-hidden="true">⋮⋮</span>
        <img class="icon" src="/imgs/svg/soccer-ball.svg" alt="⚽" />
        <span class="body">
          <span class="subtitle-hand">si ya tienes clientes</span>
          <span class="title">Cómo dar el pelotazo y vivir chill</span>
        </span>
        <span class="badge">gratis</span>
        <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </main>

  <script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sortablejs@1.15.2/Sortable.min.js"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    Sortable.create(document.querySelector(".blocks"), {
      handle: ".handle",
      animation: 150,
      ghostClass: "block--ghost",
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
